  "title": "Advances in Always Encrypted and Transparent Data Encryption",
  "contentHtml": "In this episode Michael talk with colleagues Pieter Vanhove&nbsp;\n                  (\n                     <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/pieter-vanhove-1756169/'><i class=\"fa-brands fa-linkedin\"></i></a>\n                     <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://twitter.com/Pieter_Vanhove'><i class=\"fa-brands fa-x-twitter\"></i></a>\n                  )                    \n               \n                  and Mirek Sztajno about recent updates to Always Encrypted and Transparent Data Encryption (TDE) in SQL Server 2022 and Azure SQL DB.\n\n                  <br><br>\n\n                  <!-- Insert episode info from rss.com into NNNNNN and TTTTTT which is the episode number and the title -->\n                  <iframe loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://player.rss.com/azsecpodcast/1222106?theme=light\" class=\"podcast-player\" title=\"The Azure Security Podcast\" frameborder=\"0\"><a href=\"https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/1222106/\">AE-TDE</a></iframe>\n\n                  <h5>Links</h5> \n                  <!-- Links to transcription and news articles -->\n                  <ul>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://aka.ms/sgx-enclaves-ga-blog'>SGX Enclaves</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://aka.ms/vbs-enclaves-ga-blog'>VBS Enclaves</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/sql/relational-databases/security/encryption/always-encrypted-enclaves?view=sql-server-ver16'>Always Encrypted with secure enclaves</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/t5/azure-sql-blog/tde-with-database-level-cmk-now-generally-available-for-azure/ba-p/3943829'>TDE with database-level CMK now generally available for Azure SQL Database</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/azure-sql/database/transparent-data-encryption-byok-database-level-overview?view=azuresql-db&branch=pr-en-us-26358'>Transparent data encryption (TDE) with customer-managed keys at the database level </a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/azure-sql/database/transparent-data-encryption-byok-database-level-basic-actions?view=azuresql&tabs=azure-cli%2Cazure-cli2'>Identity and key management for TDE with database level customer-managed keys </a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/azure-sql/database/transparent-data-encryption-byok-cross-tenant?view=azuresql'>Cross-tenant customer-managed keys with transparent data encryption </a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/azure-sql/database/transparent-data-encryption-byok-database-level-geo-replication-restore?view=azuresql&tabs=azure-cli%2Cazure-cli2'>Configure geo replication and backup restore for transparent data encryption with database level customer-managed keys </a></li>\n                  </ul>"
